      Craigslist sites cover large regions instead of individual metropolitan
      areas—for example, the U.S. states of Delaware and Wyoming, the Colorado
      Western Slope, the California Gold Country, and the Upper Peninsula of
      Michigan are among the locations with their own Craigslist sites.[7]
